COLOMBIA; HUMAN RIGHTS -- EL SALVADOR; HUMAN RIGHTS -- PERU; HUMAN RIGHTS -- 
ETHIOPIA; HUMAN RIGHTS -- BURMA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
