<DATE>
<P>
March 3, 1989, Friday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 9A; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
