<P>
Photo, Sheri Rhyne, left, of Canyon High School maneuvers around Kristen 
McDonald of Valencia to take rebound during 4-AA final. ; Photo, Christa 
McDonald of Valencia (30) grabs rebound despite efforts of Keri Erkenbrack. DON 
TORMEY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
